      <title>聯準會威廉斯表示前景不確定，數據將推動利率決定</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/feds-williams-said-outlook-uncertain-data-will-drive-rate-decisions-2024-04-11/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[紐約聯儲行長約翰威廉斯週四表示，聯準會在降低通膨方面取得了相當大的進展，同時指出不確定的前景意味著聯準會必須關注即將公佈的數據來制定利率政策。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/feds-williams-said-outlook-uncertain-data-will-drive-rate-decisions-2024-04-11/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 12:49:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
